title: Palomino Bar
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Jan 2014 reported revamped restaurant and expanded menu to more than bar food. Food is made from scratch and sometimes has vegan hand pies or a vegan dessert. Reported also keeps a vegan deep fryer for its Southern fried tofu and toffalo wings. Please call to confirm!
